print(dfrapt3)

# https://realpython.com/pandas-merge-join-and-concat/
# concatenated = pandas.concat([df1, df2])
# making a new df that will have all the data
dfrapt0831 = pd.concat([dfrapt0827, dfrapt3])
print(dfrapt0831)
